overview: Manuel confiscates Kasey's phone and threatens to show its contents to her mother. Kasey gets defensive as Manuel finds naked pictures on it. Once he gets a look of her hot naked body, there is no going back!  Erik asks Carmen to do a last minute babysitting gig for him while his daughter is out. Carmen soon finds out that she's out sl--ping with her crush, so she uses Erik to get some revenge.  Nickey sneaks into her teacher's classroom to find a test she had done earlier that day. A half asl--p Kurt confesses he stares at her from his desk, and she wakes him up in the best way possible.  Miley and Tommy are hanging out by the pool when Miley admits that she likes him. Tommy is quick to show how big of a crush on her he has as well.
title: Corrupt Schoolgirls 9
